      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a bit concerning to hear. When you say Case B faces \"harsher scrutiny\" and has a \"higher level of societal risk,\" are you saying the legal system inherently treats people from certain neighborhoods more severely? How much of that is based on the actual criminal behavior vs. just their socioeconomic background?",
